Silksworn					KEY:Occultist Archetype ~ Silksworn					CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.OccultistArchetype																									DESCISPI:YES	SOURCEPAGE:p.29	DESC:Occultists who recognize that flashy garb and fashionable accoutrements can be just as powerful as psychically charged relics in the right situations are known as silksworn. They draw their power from wearing luxurious garments and can be found in many noble courts throughout Golarion, though they often keep their abilities secret. Silksworn are even found among the mystics and the magical practitioners of Nex, each seeking the patronage of one or more of the Arclords.																																																																																												PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Occultist Archetype ~ Silksworn],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Occultist_Archetype_ClassSkills=True,Occultist_Archetype_Spells=True,Occultist_Archetype_Implements=True,Occultist_Archetype_Knacks=True,Occultist_Archetype_MentalFocus=True,Occultist_Archetype_WeaponandArmorProficiency=True,Occultist_Archetype_Implements=True,Occultist_Archetype_OutsideContact=True,Occultist_Archetype_MagicCircles=True,Occultist_Archetype_BindingCircles=True,Occultist_Archetype_FastCircles=True,Occultist_Archetype_ImplementMastery=True]		ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Spells|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Implements|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Cantrips|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Mental Focus|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Devoted Mystic|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Silksworn Eloquence|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=8	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Silksworn Deception|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=12	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Silksworn Arcana|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=16	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Silksworn ~ Implement Mastery|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=20		FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_Spells|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_Implements|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_Knacks|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_MentalFocus|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_WeaponandArmorProficiency|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_Implements|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_OutsideContact|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_MagicCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_BindingCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_FastCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ImplementMastery|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_WeaponandArmorProficiency|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_OutsideContact|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_MagicCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_BindingCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_FastCircles|true		COST:0

